{"about_the_game":"5 on 5 Pro Basketball born from the golden era of sports games. This spiritual successor to the 8-bit ballers bridges the gap between retro and today\u2019s simulation games.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819630/extras/Flow_BBC-3.gif?t=1635752461\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Side-scrolling, sweaty arcade action<br></li><li>Simplified 3-button gameplay<br></li><li>Decades of rosters with 175+ teams<br></li><li>1000+ players with individualized attributes <br></li><li>Seamless play calling<br></li><li>Sensational cut scenes<br></li><li>1-Player Story Mode unlocks secret teams<br></li><li>Scream-inducing local multiplayer<br></li><li>Retro vibes galore<br></li><li>No virtual currency. No pay-to-win. No micro transactions. Ever.</li></ul><br>Side-scrolling, arcade action is paired with on-the-fly strategy. 3 button gameplay is easy to pick up, but it is the dynamic play-calling that elevates this title beyond just long bombs and acrobatics.<br><br>Attribute-rich players make up a vast set of rosters. Dig through decades of teams to find your favorite All-Stars and even unlock the &quot;Legends&quot; in an immersive story mode.<br><br>This game is a passion project for us indie developers here at Namo Gamo. We hope you can feel the love put into every pixel, the endless adjustments to stat-driven gameplay, and the genuinely retro sound and music.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Legends Unlocked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/819630/abc423bd6c36ddf440388bac4ec04920a1495485.jpg"},{"name":"Phantom 5 Unlocked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/819630/8ce069544f3d392a4dd8d2274af6a83b176ae243.jpg"},{"name":"Superstars Unlocked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/819630/92c9b72bb5c39990d45fc1ed739158e3aaca1c94.jpg"},{"name":"Rookie Season Comp